    <abstract>
      <t>   This documents defines how to use the Address Family Identifier (AFI)
   17 "Distinguished Names" in LISP.  Distinguished Names can be used
   either in Endpoint Identifiers (EID) records or Routing Locators
   (RLOC) records in LISP control messages to convey additional
   information.


	 </t>
